                    <span>I once thought Balto (He is a hero too) was the hero of the Serum Run, but now, I know it's Togo.  All those brave dogs deserve recognition, but Togo's story deserves to be better-known.  Go, Togo!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Pictures sell the book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
